Interface IDawgNodeFactory<NodeType extends IDawgNode<NodeType>>

  • Type Parameters:

    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DawgNodeFactory

    public interface IDawgNodeFactory<NodeType extends IDawgNode<NodeType>>
    Builds nodes for use in DAWG structures. Implementations may do such things as manage object pools, etc.
